A classic rendition of zm lila panic


Background:
This map is a built from scratch version of zm lila panic that introduces many new elements to the classic style. For one the map has a newer theme and newer gameplay features. The underground allows for more camping spots and areas to hide out of plain site.

Support:
Cubemaps, FPS (Hints/Skips, Area Protals,Func_occluder), Spawnpoints 64, Skybox

Change Log:
  • [ADDED] - Radar
  • [ADDED] - Button to secret room by T-spawn
  • [ADDED] - Custom texture
  • [ADDED] - Decals outside
  • [ADDED] - Func_Areaportal / func_occluder
  • [ADDED] - Ambient Sound
  • [ADDED] - Skybox
  • [ADDED] - Nodraw to bottom of the map (Helps Optimization)
  • [ADDED] - Vent opening to basement area
  • [ADJUSTED] - iSETHEN sign (Now says sethen)
  • [ADJUSTED] - button to basement (No longer moves when pushed)
  • [ADJUSTED] - CT-spawn height (Prevent glitching)
  • [ADJUSTED] - Weapon room / Added 600 ammo to all weapons
  • [ADJUSTED] - Textures in secret room by T-spawn
  • [ADJUSTED] - Window on 3rd floor of lila tower (Humans can now cade)
  • [ADJUSTED] - Both barricading rooms outside on surrounding walls
  • [ADJUSTED] - roof boundaries (Allowing people to camp)
  • [ADJUSTED] - Secret AK-47 color sprites
  • [ADJUSTED] - Displacements outside
  • [ADJUSTED] - Cubemaps
  • [FIXED] - light bleeding in underground room

A few secrets I published :
1. Touch right side of the top-right wheel of the flipped track, it's a teleport to my name (see picture 2)
2. On top of my name run to the C of CoMaNdO and jump forward - It'll teleport you to the roof, the roof has a few controls to block that teleport and a few more secrets. (Note that blocking the teleport still lets zombies pass if they jump on top of each other)
